  "id": 2005048,
  "description": "When a proxy filter is registered, we now require speculative connection requests to provide a notification callback (see Bug 1943804). This breaks callers that don\u2019t supply one ([example](https://searchfox.org/firefox-main/rev/16b037c409dcd2e6dca11e0ce61384bc52dbb78d/docshell/base/nsDocShell.cpp#14038)).\nThis bug aims to ensure a callback is provided wherever possible.",
